Rangers Soccer Fans Get Away-Match Ban, Club Fined Over Sectarian Chanting

-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 
2011-04-28T17:33:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-28/rangers-soccer-fans-get-away-match-ban-club-fined-over-sectarian-chanting.html
Glasgow soccer team Rangers said
its fans were given a one-match away ban by European ruling body
UEFA for sectarian chanting at a game against  PSV Eindhoven .
Another one-game penalty was suspended. In addition the club was
fined 40,000 euros ($59,000).  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  